# Welcome to the Next.js Frontend Service

This service provides a modern Next.js 15 frontend application with:

- **App Router** — file-based routing with layouts and server components
- **TypeScript** — full type safety
- **Tailwind CSS v4** — utility-first CSS with the latest engine
- **Server Components** — React Server Components by default
- **Hot-reload** — instant feedback during development via codefly watcher

## Development

```bash
codefly run
```

## Build

The service builds as a standalone Docker image for production deployment.
